    <string name="rules_title">How to Play</string>
    <string name="rules_body">D20 Pig is a risk-and-reward dice game.\n\n1. Players alternate turns. You go first.\n\n2. On your turn, roll the 20-sided die.\n\n3. Roll 2–20: The value is added to your turn total. Choose to Roll Again or Hold.\n\n4. Roll 1: You lose your entire turn total! Your turn ends.\n\n5. Hold: Your turn total is banked to your permanent score. Your turn ends.\n\n6. First player to reach 100 points wins!\n\nStrategy tip: The higher your turn total, the more you risk losing. Know when to hold!</string>
